Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time spent on cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between the beginning of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' for cases where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' occurs

Name: Average resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for resubmission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' leading to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in resubmitted cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for cases to be finalized after 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities following 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' until case closure
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time before 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to next 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Payment Handled' in cases where payment is eventually made
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' before successful payment request
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'
